Bring "math-tools.271"

Teach Send Later using Outbox and Value
  Send Value to Outbox
  Success "sent"

Make Number be Use Triple with 9
Say "triple is {Number}"

Make Box be New Box with Value be Number
Say Use Label of Box

Make Outbox be New Channel of Int with Capacity be 2
Make Worker be Spawn Use Send Later with Outbox and 271
Make Message be Await Receive from Outbox as Maybe Int
Make Result be Await Worker

Say "message {Message}"
Say Result
Use Close of Outbox
